00:08.645 --> 00:10.278
We're here
from Marla Bay Real Estate.

00:10.280 --> 00:12.614
Scotty Lockhart,
he asked us to let him know

00:12.616 --> 00:14.682
what we thought we could
put it on the market for.

00:14.684 --> 00:16.518
This is my place.
It's not for sale.

00:16.520 --> 00:18.219
This is fucking bullshit.
Don't ever do that again.

00:18.221 --> 00:20.187
No, no, no. Listen to me, okay?
I've got something for us.

00:20.189 --> 00:22.424
You could invest
half of your profit in this

00:22.426 --> 00:24.358
and you would still be
doing great.

00:24.360 --> 00:25.693
You know what, Scotty?

00:25.695 --> 00:27.662
I need to go.
I'm late for work.

00:27.664 --> 00:30.531
Uh, you two know each other
or something?

00:30.533 --> 00:32.198
Mind if I sit here
for a drink?

00:32.200 --> 00:33.300
Sure.

00:33.302 --> 00:34.701
I'm not my brother.

00:34.703 --> 00:37.404
Just thought you should
know that.

00:37.406 --> 00:38.806
Okay.

00:38.808 --> 00:40.541
I read your book, Noah.

00:40.543 --> 00:43.043
I'm sex. I'm the reason
the word was invented.

00:43.045 --> 00:44.711
No marriage could
survive me?

00:44.713 --> 00:46.814
Before you judge, will you
please just read the whole book?

00:46.816 --> 00:48.849
We end up together.
It's a happy ending.

00:48.851 --> 00:51.051
Wasn't that the end that Harry
wants you to change?

00:51.053 --> 00:52.753
You fucked her, didn't you?

00:52.755 --> 00:54.488
This is the problem.
You're a goddamn narcissist.

00:54.490 --> 00:57.223
It's all about your pain,
your loss, your kid!

00:57.225 --> 00:59.059
Cole!

00:59.061 --> 01:00.994
I blew up my life
for you, Alison.

01:00.996 --> 01:03.096
I don't belong to you.
We're not living in your book.

01:03.098 --> 01:05.698
You can't control me.

01:09.103 --> 01:11.704
I'm pregnant.

01:11.706 --> 01:14.807
I got a lead recently
from a guy who claims to have

01:14.809 --> 01:17.477
a piece of evidence that could
blow this whole case wide open.

01:17.479 --> 01:19.545
Why doesn't he just
call the police?

01:19.547 --> 01:21.214
The police won't pay him.

